'''凡妮莎·雷'''（{{lang-en|Vanessa Ray}}，{{bd|1981年|6月24日}}）<ref>[http://hollywoodlife.com/celeb/vanessa-ray/# "Vanessa Ray"] {{Wayback|url=http://hollywoodlife.com/celeb/vanessa-ray/ |date=20171207015447 }}. HollywoodLife.com. Retrieved September 8, 2015.</ref>，是一位[[美國|美國]]女演員和歌手，以代表作《[[美少女的謊言|美少女的謊言]]》及《[[惡靈嬰弒|惡靈嬰弒]]》系列而知名。

==個人生活==
雷現在生活和工作兩者分別在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]和[[紐約市|紐約市]]，2003年1月8日她嫁給演員Derek James Baynham<ref>[http://www.aoltv.com/show/marriage-under-construction-1/7984186 "Marriage Under Construction 1"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aoltv.com/show/marriage-under-construction-1/7984186 |date=20140518180218 }}. HuffPost TV. Retrieved February 27, 2015.</ref><ref>Nevada Marriage Index 1966–2005, Nevada State Health Division, Office of Vital Records, Carson City, Nevada.</ref>，2007年，HGTV系列正在建設的第一個賽季捂著購房及裝修，並最終出售房子在[[多倫多|多倫多]]<ref>[http://www.thestar.com/news/2007/11/03/survivor_the_toronto_house_hunt.html "Survivor: the Toronto house hunt"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/2007/11/03/survivor_the_toronto_house_hunt.html |date=20160305075720 }}. Toronto Star. November 3, 2007.</ref><ref>[http://www.hgtv.ca/marriageunderconstruction/episodes/ "Marriage Under Construction - Episodes - HGTV Canada"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hgtv.ca/marriageunderconstruction/episodes/ |date=20160613212600 }}. hgtv.ca. Retrieved February 27, 2015.</ref>。一段時間後，兩人於2009年離婚。
2015年3月，雷在Instagram和Twitter上宣布，她和她訂婚六年的男友蘭登·比爾德<ref>[http://us.hellomagazine.com/celebrities/1201503133176/exclusive-blue-bloods-star-vanessa-ray-is-engaged "Exclusive: 'Blue Bloods' star Vanessa Ray is engaged!"] {{Wayback|url=http://us.hellomagazine.com/celebrities/1201503133176/exclusive-blue-bloods-star-vanessa-ray-is-engaged |date=20160808013036 }}. Hello magazine. March 13, 2015.</ref>，他們並於2015年6月14日在加州結婚。<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3127479/Pretty-Little-Liars-star-Vanessa-Ray-marries-musician-Landon-Beard-fun-filled-wedding-group-singing-tacos.html "Vanessa Ray marries musician Landon Beard at fun wedding with singing and tacos"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3127479/Pretty-Little-Liars-star-Vanessa-Ray-marries-musician-Landon-Beard-fun-filled-wedding-group-singing-tacos.html |date=20160118101439 }}. Mail Online.</ref>

